_refine.details                                  
;Bulk solvent terms included in Fob file created with standard X-PLOR script.

Residues simultaneously refined in two or more conformations are:
Gln50, Leu67, Ser88, Ser110, Ser170,Ser236, the non=amidine part of the inhibitor.

Disordered waters are: 
HOH296 which is close to HOH564;
HOH459 which is close to a symmetry-related equivalent of itself;

His91 is MONOPROTONATED ON THE EPSILON NITROGEN.
His40 and HIS57 are DIPROTONATED.
;
